quran[23{c,v,t}:
89,1,Wal-Fajr
89,2,Wa layaalin 'ashr
89,3,Wash shaf'i wal watr
89,4,Wallaili izaa yasr
89,5,Hal fee zaalika qasamul lizee hijr
89,6,Alam tara kaifa fa'ala rabbuka bi'aad
89,7,Iramaa zaatil 'imaad
89,8,Allatee lam yukhlaq misluhaa fil bilaad
89,9,Wa samoodal lazeena jaabus sakhra bil waad
89,10,Wa fir'awna zil awtaad
89,11,Allazeena taghaw fil bilaad
89,12,Fa aksaroo feehal fasaad
89,13,Fasabba 'alaihim Rabbuka sawta 'azaab
89,14,Inna Rabbaka labil mirsaad
89,15,Fa ammal insaanu izaa mab talaahu Rabbuhoo fa akramahoo wa na' 'amahoo fa yaqoolu Rabbeee akraman
89,16,Wa ammaaa izaa mabtalaahu faqadara 'alaihi rizqahoo fa yaqoolu Rabbeee ahaanan
89,17,Kalla bal laa tukrimooo nal yateem
89,18,Wa laa tahaaaddoona 'alaata'aamil miskeen
89,19,Wa taakuloonat turaasa aklal lammaa
89,20,Wa tuhibboonal maala hubban jammaa
89,21,Kallaaa izaaa dukkatil ardu dakkan dakka
89,22,Wa jaaa'a Rabbuka wal malaku saffan saffaa
89,23,Wa jeee'a yawma'izim bi jahannnam; Yawma 'iziny yatazakkarul insaanu wa annaa lahuz zikraa
